             sworn. - I took charge of the prisoner; he confessed he had only bought a pint of varnish instead of a quart; I was present when the bottles were found in the foot.</p>
               <p>Mr. Cary. I have no doubt these are my bottles.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I have lived with my master six years, I know nothing of the property.</p>
